sub_title: Senior Consultant Organization Transformation - Major Programmes at Deloitte
summary:
First and foremost, I love to make a difference. In the lives of others, in the world and to the complex issues we face today. 

I have been working towards this goal for more than five years as project manager in the field of international cooperation, humanitarian aid and human rights. I enjoy working together with a team towards developing the resilience of and protecting vulnerable communities.  

Working towards concrete and pragmatic milestones gives me energy. I am highly organized and truly dedicated to get the job done and I am committed to work tirelessly for a team and the goals set. 

I have a broad and international interest and in my time-off you can find me swimming or running, surrounded by friends or supporting communities through volunteer work.
